FBIS4-63057 "drsov097_b_94025" FBIS-SOV-94-097 Daily Report 18 May 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Edict Establishes Russian Postal Service Day Yeltsin Edict Establishes Russian Postal Service Day MK1805124394 Moscow NEZAVISIMAYA GAZETA in Russian 18 May 94 p 2 MK1805124394 Moscow NEZAVISIMAYA GAZETA Russian BFN [RIA report under the "In Brief" rubric] [Text] Moscow -- A new holiday -- Day of the Russian Postal Service -- has been established by Boris Yeltsin's edict. It will be marked on the second Sunday in July.
